Ingredients:
3 eggs
Milk
Butter
Chives
Smoked salmon
Muffin/roll/bread
Salad

Method:
Melt butter in bowl
Add eggs and beat
Add splash/glug of milk
Add chives
Cover bowl with plate and microwave for 5 mins or so
Halfway through stir a bit
Is ready when solid but fluffy throughout
Will get very hot and steamy
Serve on bread with salmon and salad
